title: Les Vues de Suisse
description: High mountains in the distance. In the foreground a stream being forded by goats, sheep, a cow and two peasants, one of whom rides a mule. In the middle ground, at left, a bridge and behind that a chapel. At the right of the latter is seen part of an aquaduct. Large trees at far right.
name: Scenic panel
